---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { BookOpen, TrendingUp, Target, Brain, FileText, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mental Health Research & Evidence-Based Practice | RealMindSolutions" description="Mental health research articles—evidence-based therapy, treatment effectiveness studies, clinical research, and the latest findings in psychology and psychiatry.">
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Mental Health Research</h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600">Evidence-based practice, treatment effectiveness, and the latest research in mental health care.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Introduction */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Evidence-based practice is the foundation of effective mental health treatment. This resource hub brings together research on therapy effectiveness, treatment outcomes, and the latest findings in psychology and psychiatry to help you make informed decisions about your mental health care.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/resources/guides/therapy-types-explained" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Brain className="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Evidence-Based Therapies</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Learn about research-supported therapy approaches like CBT, DBT, EMDR, and their effectiveness for different conditions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Explore Therapies
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/learn/statistics" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <TrendingUp className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Mental Health Statistics</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Data and statistics on mental health prevalence, treatment access, and outcomes.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            View Statistics
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy-types" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Target className="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Treatment Effectiveness</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Research on what treatments work best for specific mental health conditions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Learn More
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Blog Articles Coming Soon */}
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Research Blog Articles</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We're building a library of research-based articles covering:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Latest mental health research findings</li>
          <li>• Therapy effectiveness studies and meta-analyses</li>
          <li>• Neurobiological basis of mental health conditions</li>
          <li>• Medication research and clinical trials</li>
          <li>• Digital mental health interventions research</li>
          <li>• Long-term outcomes of different treatments</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Explore our existing evidence-based resources above, or browse related tags below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Related Tags */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Topics</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy-types" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapy Types</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/policy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Policy</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/mental-health" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Mental Health</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
